# Interview Review Pipeline

- Keep raw interview transcript review in `server/interviewReview/`; do not scatter prompt, chunk, merge, or schema logic into unrelated files.
- `InterviewReviewJSON v1` is a local import path. It must bypass LLM calls and only normalize schema.
- Raw transcripts must not silently fall back to regex Q/A rules. If AI is unavailable or returns no valid reviewed Q/A, return an explicit failed status with empty `qaPairs`.
- Chunk boundaries should prefer speaker/question turns and use overlap; merge logic owns deduplication across overlap.
- When changing the AI contract, update `docs/interview-review-pipeline.md` and add/adjust coverage in `server/check.mjs`.
